<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ ài wǒ men 迦南815</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ ài wǒ men, tuán jù wǒ men, yòng tā zì jǐ de bǎo xuè xǐ jìng wǒ men de zuì.
 wǒ men chéng wèi shén de ér nǚ, hé děng róng yào, hé děng yǒu fú.
 kàn nǎ zhǔ kuài yào jià yún jiàng lín, de shàng de wàn zú dōu yào yīn tā āi kū.
 zhǐ yīn tā men yuǎn lí zhēn shén, bù jìng bài zào wù zhī zhǔ.
 shén de ér nǚ men a, shén de ér nǚ men, yào jǐn shǒu wǒ men suǒ xìn de.
 kàn shǒu pú táo yuán, qín ná xiǎo hú lí, zhǔ bì suí shí yǐn dǎo nǐ.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>815</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>